* Statistics: Displays participant statistics by various categories.
*   When to use:    Before or after the race to review participant demographics.
*   How to use:     Double-click to display statistics for all categories.
*   Customize:      Comment out (*) any categories you don't need, or add new ones.

Statistics.rsm      RACE
Statistics.rsm      DIV
Statistics.rsm      SEX
Statistics.rsm      AGE

* Additional categories:
* Statistics.rsm    CITY
* Statistics.rsm    STATE
* Statistics.rsm    CLUB
* Statistics.rsm    TSHIRT